{"Id":350000370,"Name":"异相·冰盈舞者","RarityId":1,"Icon":"https://api.encore.moe/resource/Data/Game/Aki/UI/UIResources/Common/Image/IconMonsterHead/T_IconMonsterHead_SG_31083_UI.png","BigIcon":"0","Tachine":"/Game/Aki/UI/UIResources/UiSingleTower/Image/T_UiSingleTowerMonster1_UI.T_UiSingleTowerMonster1_UI","ElementIdArray":[1],"MonsterEntityID":"","MonsterPose":"0","UndiscoveredDes":"以冰为裙的类人残象，动作轻盈优雅。","DiscoveredDes":"该敌人<span style=\"color:#a2fbfc;\">冷凝伤害</span><span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">抗性提高</span>。<br>以冰为裙的类人残象，动作轻盈优雅。脚下锋利的冰刃既是它模仿人类花滑姿态的工具，也是撕裂敌人的利器。它能敏锐地感受冰面上的一切变化，一望无际冰面就如它的双眼。于是它便通过冰面的倒影将人类的花滑姿态尽收眼底，不断学习、模仿，并运用到自己的攻击手段中，不知不觉中，它将人类花样滑冰的崇高艺术演绎成了一场寂静无声的死亡之舞。","PerchId":[13],"Properties":{},"GrowthRates":{},"Rarity":"轻波级","Element":{"Id":1,"Name":"冷凝","Icon":"https://api.encore.moe/resource/Data/Game/Aki/UI/UIResources/Common/Image/IconElementRound/T_IconElementIce1_UI.png"}}